data.description: This wonderful quad-style townhome is move-in ready! Several updates through the years. New siding, and storm door. Newer furnace, water heater and garage door. You will love the location of this home being on the end of a private street and backing up to a beautiful wetland area. The spacious kitchen has an abundance of maple cabinets, a center island, and newer stainless-steel appliances. One of the best features on the main level is the sunroom. With the large windows and SE exposure you won’t lack for light. The upstairs loft is a great space for a home office and even has a balcony looking over the wetland area. You couldn’t ask for more in a location - parks, shopping, restaurants, and proximity to 494. Now is your time to enjoy maintenance-free living and everything Plymouth has to offer! Wayzata schools a plus.
